# Language: English Only

This project is conducted entirely in English.

- **Code**: Variable names, function names, file names — use English
- **Comments**: Inline, JSDoc, block comments — use English
- **UI**: Labels, buttons, messages, placeholders, tooltips — use English
- **API**: Endpoint paths, response keys, error messages — use English

When adding or modifying code, keep all identifiers, strings, and comments in English.
